Package com.lugowoy.helper.filling.array.points

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FillingArrayPoints<T extends java.lang.Number>
    The interface declares a contract to implement the filling of an objects of Array and classical array objects of the Point class with coordinates of a numerical type.
    FillingArrayPointsArrayNumbers<T extends java.lang.Number>
    The functional interface declares a contract to filling an array of an object of the Point class by initializing the coordinates of the points with the numeric values of the array.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FillerArrayPoints<T extends java.lang.Number>
    The class is the inheritor of the class FillerArray.
    FillingArrayPointsRandomDoubleNumbers
    Created by Konstantin Lugowoy on 15-Jan-18.
    FillingArrayPointsRandomIntegerNumbers
    The class implements the contract declared by the FillingArrayPoints interface.
    FillingArrayPointsReadDoubleNumbers
    The class is the heir of the FillingArrayPointsReadValues class and implements it's contract.
    FillingArrayPointsReadIntegerNumbers
    The class is the heir of the FillingArrayPointsReadValues class and implements it's contract.
    FillingArrayPointsReadValues<T extends java.lang.Number>
    The class is the root of the class hierarchy that implements the contract declared in the FillingArrayPoints interface of the filling of objects of Array class and classical arrays with an object of the Point class with numeric coordinates using the data read by the object of the class Reader encapsulated in this class.
